div.p: The modelled projections are available through the Tasmanian Partnership for Advanced Computing (TPAC) portal ( https://dl.tpac.org.au/tpacportal/). The TasVeg vegatation layers can be found at http://maps.thelist.tas.gov.au/. No other data were used in the analyses, which were produced using a freely available Species Distribution Model, MAXENT.
